title: Budget for your Self Assessment tax bill if you're self-employed

heading_context: Budget for your Self Assessment tax bill if you're self-employed
chunks.html_content:
Use the self-employed ready reckoner to budget for your Self Assessment tax bill for the 2023 to 2024 tax year.

Enter your estimated weekly or monthly profit to get an idea of how much Income Tax, Class 2 and Class 4 National Insurance you’ll pay.
